(secondQuint)A Study in the Use of Home Blood Pressure Monitoring and Telephone Follow-up to Control Blood Pressure.

 Participants will all have home blood pressure monitors, education session on controlling their blood pressure and will be randomized to recieve 6 months of intensive telephonic on a set monitoring schedule or no telephonic follow up.

 Phone calls will be weekly for 4 weeks, then every 2 weeks for 8 weeks then monthly for 3 months.

